headline: Northrop Grumman Stock Flies To Highs Alongside Power Distributor, Foods Contractor
summary: Meanwhile, a government-contract win helped propel US Foods Holding to a record high and power distributor Powell Industries reached a price peak.  High-tech weapons maker Northrop Grumman notched a high above 666 as it pushed toward its third consecutive gain.  The stock was still in a buy zone, up to 672.94.
